original_title: 10 Minute Solution - Belly, Butt And Thigh Blasters
overview: Jessica Smith presents five ten-minute workouts designed to fit into even the busiest of schedules. Workouts are: 'Better Booty Camp', 'Strong and Slim Thighs', 'Trim and Toned Tummy', 'Lower Body Makeover' and 'Belly Flab Fighter'.
title: 10 Minute Solution - Belly, Butt And Thigh Blasters
